about.summary: Click params for commmand line interfaces to GeoJSON.

name: cligj
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "0.4.0" %}

package:
  name: cligj
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: cligj-0.4.0.tar.gz
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/c/cligj/cligj-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 12ad07994f5c1173b06087ffbaacec52f9ebe4687926e5aacfc22b6b0c8b3f54

build:
  number: 0
  script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record record.txt

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - setuptools
    - click >=4.0
  run:
    - python
    - click >=4.0

test:
  imports:
    - cligj

about:
  home: https://github.com/mapbox/cligj
  license: BSD 3-Clause
  license_file: '{{ environ["RECIPE_DIR"] }}/LICENSE'
  summary: 'Click params for commmand line interfaces to GeoJSON.'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - ocefpaf
